O. L. LA BUDDE, as Collector, etc., v. CUDAHY BROTHERS COMPANY. No. 5689. Circuit Court of Appeals, Seventh Circuit. Feb. 11, 1936. B. J. Husting, of Milwaukee, Wis., for appellant. James D. Shaw, of Milwaukee, Wis., for appellee.

Before EVANS and SPARKS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

On motion of counsel for appellee, it is now here ordered, adjudged, and decreed by this court that this appeal be, and the same is hereby, dismissed.
